---
title: Honey Mustard Salmon with Roasted Asparagus and Israeli Couscous Pilaf
description: There are 3 reasons why this dish make us (o)mega happy: 1) tender salmon is chock-full of healthy fats, 2) honey and mustard are a sweet and tangy match made in heaven, and 3) cooking couscous in veggie stock enhances the flavor without increasing the calories. Talk about a trifecta!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/maple-mustard-salmon-788b5d04.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/maple-mustard-salmon-88b201dc.pdf
